Delivery Policy Instacoins / Delivery Policy

Instacoins will send Bitcoin to the address you specify within 10 minutes of an authorized withdrawal, but receipt of such Bitcoin will depend on the speed of the underlying network, more commonly referred to as the blockchain.

Please allow for 6 network confirmations for the funds to be credited to the address you specified. You can track the progress of your transaction by clicking on the Wallet Address in My Account or Transaction History, or by visiting www.blockchain.com/btc/address/ *your wallet address*
